des: Philly Beer Garden Skill will help you find the nearest (or dearest) beer garden, where you can enjoy a frosty draft under the sun or a stiff cocktail under the stars. With so many new gardens opening up this summer, our skill is making it simpler to find one that's right for you and your merry band of imbibers.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
